cf3e0d48-5ea0-4329-8276-92cdaff6dadd.label: Define Ring Value Mapping by Range
cf3e0d48-5ea0-4329-8276-92cdaff6dadd.title: Define Ring Value Mapping by Range
cf3e0d48-5ea0-4329-8276-92cdaff6dadd.description:
Define Ring Value Mapping by Range
for properties of type number or date/time allow a ring to be derived on a range:
if property value is between X and Y then this Ring is allocated

for example: if date is > 12 months in the past, is between 6-12 months in the past, is less than 6 months ago
or:
if effort > 10 then ring = HUGE
else if 5 < effort < 10 then ring = Substantial
...

a9f4615c-7afc-4e31-a2ad-8ab5b371c9d7.title: Define Ring Value Mapping from Expression
a9f4615c-7afc-4e31-a2ad-8ab5b371c9d7.description:
Allow an expression to be defined that turns the value(s) of  one or more properties into a ring

For example: $type=="ui"?"ui":($status=="done"?"extra":"black")

Upload previously Downloaded files 

- handle upload data: 
  - overwrite
  - add new (object type, rating type, template, objects, ratings, viewpoint) - no updating existing 
  - merge: create new blips and ratings for uploaded ones when colliding (AND some form of change between rating objects?)

          - take the most recently changed object
